---
import MaterialArrowOutwardSharp from '~icons/material-symbols/arrow-outward-sharp'
---

<div
  class="relative bg-background-secondary px-12 md:px-24 pt-12 pb-0 overflow-hidden aug-expeditions mb-48"
  data-augmented-ui="tr-clip bl-clip t-clip-x bl-clip-x br-2-clip-y both"
>
  <div class="mb-12">
    <!-- Title stacked -->
    <h2 class="text-foreground text-5xl font-display max-w-xs mb-8">Countdown to Singularity</h2>

    <!-- Description paragraph -->
    <p class="text-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed font-mono max-w-sm mb-6">
      Much like a black holeâ€™s gravitational pull, which grows exponentially stronger near its event horizon, the
      Technological Singularity describes a future where AI surpasses human intelligence, triggering rapid,
      uncontrollable progress. This self-improving AI creates a feedback loop, compressing vast advancements into
      moments, reshaping reality beyond prediction or comprehension, akin to crossing an inescapable cosmic threshold.
    </p>

    <div class="lg:absolute top-12 right-12 md:right-24">
      <div class="w-full">
        <a
          href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Technological_singularity"
          target="_blank"
          class="text-foreground text-sm font-mono hover:text-link-primary-hover transition-colors duration-300 uppercase inline-flex items-center gap-2"
        >
          <MaterialArrowOutwardSharp className="w-6 h-6" />
          <div class="flex items-center gap-0">
            <span aria-hidden="true" class="font-mono">
              {'['}
            </span>
            READ MORE
            <span aria-hidden="true" class="font-mono">
              {']'}
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Timeline -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-8 xl:grid-cols-7 items-end gap-8 lg:gap-4 lg:pr-32 xl:pr-48">
    <!-- First paper of AI -->
    <div class="w-full lg:col-span-2 xl:col-span-2 flex gap-4 border-t border-foreground pt-4 lg:h-32">
      <h2 class="text-foreground text-sm font-mono">2027</h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Today -->
    <div class="w-full lg:col-span-2 xl:col-span-2 flex border-t border-foreground pt-4 h-auto lg:h-44 xl:h-48">
      <h2 class="text-foreground text-sm font-mono">2030</h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Singularity -->
    <div
      class="w-full lg:col-span-4 xl:col-span-3 flex flex-col gap-4 border-t border-foreground pt-4 h-56 sm:h-72 md:h-120 lg:h-64 xl:h-72 2xl:h-92 overflow-hidden"
    >
      <div class="text-foreground text-sm font-mono">Singularity</div>

      <div class="relative overflow-hidden">
        <svg class="w-fitbbox font-flex" data-fitbbox-ha="7.1" aria-label="Embrace the Future">
          <text transform="translate(-1,-3.43)">45</text>
        </svg>

        <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-t from-background-secondary to-transparent">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .aug-expeditions {
    --aug-tr: var(--aug-size) !important;
    --aug-bl: var(--aug-size) !important;
    --aug-tl: var(--aug-size) !important;
    --aug-t: var(--aug-size) !important;
    --aug-br: var(--aug-size) !important;
    --aug-border-all: 0px !important;
    --aug-inlay-all: 0px !important;
    --aug-border-bg: var(--background) !important;
    --aug-inlay-bg: var(--background-secondary) !important;
  }
</style>
